# LLM Studio Roadmap

## Phase 1: Platform Development and Launch (Q3 2024)
- Development of core functionalities including dashboard, automation, and multi-network support.
- Internal and beta testing with select Web3 projects.
- Official public launch of the platform.

## Phase 2: Feature Expansion and User Growth (Q4 2024)
- Introduction of advanced analytics and real-time project monitoring.
- Implementation of enhanced security protocols like multi-factor authentication.
- Expansion of supported blockchain networks.
- Release of comprehensive documentation and onboarding materials.

## Phase 3: Community Building and Ecosystem Integration (Q1 2025)
- Launch community forums and support channels.
- Develop plugin and API capabilities to allow third-party integrations.
- Form strategic partnerships within the Web3 ecosystem.

## Phase 4: Long-term Enhancements and AI Integration (Mid 2025 and beyond)
- Ongoing platform optimization driven by user feedback and industry trends.
- Exploration and integration of AI-powered project management tools.
- Expansion into full lifecycle management for decentralized application development.

This roadmap guides LLM Studioâ€™s growth to maintain relevance and provide lasting value as the Web3 landscape evolves.